Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:43.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Nice angle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I couldn't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:59.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you were standing\Nin a prearranged spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:03.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that was\Na coincidence, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:07.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.\NIt was a good view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:11.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who\Ngot the good view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to\Ngive you a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:34.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:37.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:39.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NJump into the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NShe's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:58.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:02.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Swim properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:07.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to, but all the water\NI've absorbed is weighing me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I was going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very cruel of you, Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was faster than\Ngetting out of my gigai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stay still for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:31.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:34.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:39.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard someone\Nfell into the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:50.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone here\Nnamed Shintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? H-Hey, Rangiku?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going to happen to me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:57.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take care...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:07.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to be\Nall right by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank you for dropping me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:25.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew... Acting like\Na stuffed animal is tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:29.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, this sure is\Nan incredibly luxurious mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:31.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This TV's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of expensive-looking\Nfurniture, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of jobs\Nher parents must have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to be able to afford these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:40.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro, sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It burns! It burns! It burns!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:02.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- It burns! It burns!\N- Shintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:18.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Shintaro!\NYou really can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:23.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry Shintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I was going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:26.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:29.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you surprised\Nthat I can move?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:37.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I've been praying to God\Nthat you'd be able to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:45.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you're the one\Nwho saved me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Shintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:02.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been together all this time.\NWhy don't you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:09.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... Umm...\NI do know your name, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:10.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:15.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fell into the river,\NI lost my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:24.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, are you\Nthe only one in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:29.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:35.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a good-for-nothing,\Nso mommy dumped him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A good-for-nothing...\NDo you understand what that means?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:45.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy is really busy and\Nshe always comes home late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:48.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I look after the house by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:52.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're so little,\Nyet so admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:53.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:55.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Shintaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:06.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I being\Ndressed like this again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not teamed up\Nwith Ichigo's sister, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:12.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:13.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,NOTE: THESE ARE RUBBER DOLLS!\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:17.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Shintaro,\Nit's time for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:22.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:36.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Uhh, well, this is... Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:45.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:51.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't last if I keep doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:56.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Shintaro, what do you\Nwant to play next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:59.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Play company? Play school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Umm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:04.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's nice today.\NWhy don't we play outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:12.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a lot more fun to run outside\Nwith your friends on a day like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:18.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:23.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And... I have no friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:32.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I understand. Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww... I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:40.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being mean, Shintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:47.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Come to think of it,\Nwhy were you outside earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:49.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hate going outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see our home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:03.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The home where I used to live\Nwith mommy, daddy, and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:05.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:10.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When mommy and daddy\Nwere friendly with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we lived in a different home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:21.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really big and really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:28.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, daddy, and I,\Nand Shintaro, a big dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We all lived together there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:34.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought I was Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a real dog called Shintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:41.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But he couldn't live\Nwith us in this house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:45.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so mommy bought me\Na stuffed animal Shintaro in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:49.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? So what happened\Nto the first Shintaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:55.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He got hit by a car and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoops... This is bad, this is bad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.21,0:10:07.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you had so much fun there.\NI'm sure you didn't want to move, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:11.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no choice...\NMommy's having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:26.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's a bit cold of her\Nto act as if nothing happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,even though you fell into the river?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:31.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I told her not to call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:38.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's working hard at her job.\NI shouldn't make her worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:44.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I'm with you,\NI can have fun without going outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This kid...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's acting tough,\Nbut she's actually lonely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She must have wanted to\Ngo to her previous home{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because she remembered\Nsomething fun that happened there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Then let's go\Nto your previous home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:02.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:22.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You lived in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:26.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like no one's living in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:31.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:35.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is this the first time\Nyou've come here since you moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:36.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:49.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro was hit by a car here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:50.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:55.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:59.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is dangerous...\NWe should get away from here quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:00.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This bad feeling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Shintaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice,\Nwe're going into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:33.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:37.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. It was planning to\Nforce us inside from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:40.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:41.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:45.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:46.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An evil spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:54.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap! Oddly, there have been\Na lot of Hollows in this town lately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is something going on\Nthat I don't know about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:02.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:08.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. We've got to\Nget away from here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap! It appeared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:29.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's just one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But now's not the time to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to let us pass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Shintaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:50.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:53.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki! You can see the Hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure... It's kind of blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't see it clearly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She can only tell\Nthat something's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:14.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:23.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what are we going to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Hollow has\Nclosed off the gate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is beating it the only option?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't chasing after us, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:43.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro, what's going on?\NI'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:51.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap. Are you serious?\NI've got to fight in this body?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:55.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki! Look for an opening\Nand run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:56.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You Hollow bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:07.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:47.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on running!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:55.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:32.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:35.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away, Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:01.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro. Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:04.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:08.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:24.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:39.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku... You're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:46.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,SHINTARO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:51.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... He...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:55.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Miyuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you wrapped up\Nin something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:05.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro, you're all in tatters...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, you're really blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:11.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:18.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who saved you back there...\NIt was the original Shintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shintaro did?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:21.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He was worried about you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:30.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:36.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:41.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was finally able to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:45.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:49.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rely on me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:55.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right. Even if I can't talk,\NI'll always be watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:59.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make some\Nother friends from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:03.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I only need you with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:10.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:11.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:14.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you're actually lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents moved\Nfor their own convenience
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and your mom is busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:23.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you try your best\Nnot to cause her trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to\Npush yourself so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:34.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Others have also flung me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:38.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was made a mod soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was abandoned at\Nsomeone else's convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that wouldn't make\Nany sense to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:50.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I felt like there was nothing\NI could do, but my friends saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:20:00.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all stupid,\Nand they're no good without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:03.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what's\Namusing about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:08.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you feel lonely,\Nmake some friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll give your mom\Nsome peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:16.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:23.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. The original Shintaro\Nand I will be watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:30.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to respond to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:32.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.49,0:20:35.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:38.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Farewell...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one thing settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:00.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! She gave me a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:04.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you help that girl so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:09.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!\NAll little kids idolize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kon, the endearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:12.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:17.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku, why are there\Nso many Hollows appearing lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more than before,\Naren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:22.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:26.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There may be a big battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:28.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki...try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:43.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NI'm going to leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:23.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I finally get to be\Nthe lead in the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.25,0:23:26.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's going to be\Nan episode where Mr. Urahara is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.47,0:23:27.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke seems like he'd\Nhave a lot of strange enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:28.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are probably\Ngoing to get troublesome
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:30.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,when some strange visitors\Nshow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:32.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,People mature when\Nthey overcome hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:34.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A story like this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:36.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:37.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:45.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, you clean up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:47.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are in the World of the Living,\Nyou're getting too lazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:53.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:55.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are to separate the trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:58.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't put everything\Ninto the same bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:00.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:02.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Start over!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.51,0:24:03.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...